results.deck: Ultra Games was a publishing-only mark for Konami on the NES and other Nintendo platforms.
results.description: Ultra Games was a publishing-only mark of Konami used in North America to get around Nintendo's regulations that placed limits on the number of games a company could publish in a year. When these restrictions were relaxed in the 1990s, such chicanery was no longer required.
results.name: Ultra Games
